																		Author Post
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610204704" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;" >sirpudding</a></span> <span class="odate time_1456698251 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">28 Feb 2016 22:24</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2464917">
									

<p>Part 4 of a series.</p>
<p>Thanks to my teammates <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458601804" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458601804" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;">GreenWolf</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458601804" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span> for brainstorming, strategy, feedback and support. Especially TyGently who made the letterhead image (and somehow managed to upload it before I could). Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2039383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458601804" alt="MrWrong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2039383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;">MrWrong</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458601804" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;">psul</a></span> for feedback in the forums.</p>
<p>ETA: How could I have forgotten the inimitable <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1458601804" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span> who made the MTF Tau-5 patch logo?</p>
<p>Other entries:<br />
1. <a href="/avatara">Avatara</a>, by A Random Day<br />
2. <a href="/grant-request-for-investigating-the-potential-application-of">GRANT REQUEST FOR INVESTIGATING THE APPLICATION OF CERTAIN RESEARCH ASSETS IN OVERCOMING INHERENT LIMITATIONS OF THE HUMAN BODY</a> by GreenWolf<br />
3. <a href="/scp-2970">SCP-2970</a>, Holy Misplacement, by TyGently<br />
4. Operation AZURE PEREGRINE, by sirpudding<br />
5. <a href="/the-lord-of-endowments">The Lord of Endowments</a> by sirpudding<br />
6. <a href="/samsara">Samsara</a> by A Random Day and TyGently</p>
<p>This represents Team Apotheosis' After Action Report entry for the <a href="/mobile-task-force-contest">Mobile Task Force Contest</a>.</p>
<p>In order to write this I needed to make an <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/local--files/operation-azure-peregrine/Tau-5%20Table%20of%20Organization.png">org chart for MTF Tau-5</a> and I'm including it in the files for reference.</p>
<p>Commentary is now available at <a href="/sirpudding-s-author-page">my author page</a>!</p>

