			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2466066">
									

<p>Without some effective countermeasures the Foundation would be unable to cope with working magic altogether (and this series takes place in a world where PL was developing commercial applications of weird science; which people actually paid for and used). If a wholly conventional team had attempted this raid, they would have just died. Eventually it would be fairly impossible for the Foundation to find people willing to go on utterly symbolic suicide missions in order to prove some ideological purity.</p>

