			<div class="content" id="post-content-2468810">
									

<p>This is super fun, high-quality technobabble. I particularly enjoyed the Banishment Grenades.</p>
<p>There were parts that were&#8230; maybe a little too bone-dry. I get that that's hard to get away from, though&#8230; One minor thing that could be done would be to break up the paragraphs more when you want to get across a sense of a faster pace. Good for action. It's a cheap little technique, but it might help a little.</p>
<p>All in all, upvoted. This was quite neat.</p>

